---
title: Beef Banh Mi Bowls with Sriracha Mayo, Carrot, and Pickled Cucumber
description: FOOD TREND RIFF COMIN’ IN HOT. We took the traditional sandwich (bread, meat, chili, carrot, pickly things, mayonnaise, and magic), lost the bread (been eating soooo many stress carbs), and threw it in our favorite eating vessel, THE BOWL. Once we looked at said bowl, filled with saucy beef, carrot, pickles, and spicy mayo, we threw back in some carbs because...life can be stressful. Hello, lime rice!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5d56b4b23ebaf5000e4c73ce-7b479bba.jpg
